---------------------------------
|  Game Manual -- GoldRau$$$ch  |
---------------------------------

In the Game "GeldRau$$$ch, (german
for money fever), you have to answer
up to 15 questions to win 1Billion 
virtual Talers.
All that you need and are
allowed to use is your general
knowledge. With increasing level the
questions become more and more
difficult. To play the game you need
a keyboard. Have Fun!

If you have questions or bugs to
report, or if you want to help me,
translating the game into more
languages, please do not hesitate
to write me an e-mail:
eckert.georg@gmx.de

GoldRau$$$ch is free and open source
software.
